headline: Jim Cramer Calls Deere’s New Long-Term Financial Forecasts “Very, Very Bullish”
summary: Deere & Company (NYSE:DE) is one of the stocks Jim Cramer expressed thoughts on. Cramer called it a “high-quality company” during the episode, as he remarked: “Deere rolled out some new long-term financial forecasts that I thought were very, very bullish.
